d you are loved. And bottom line, is your problem is important to you, it''s important to them.', 4609, 0), (180377, 'Love is your religion', 33183, 0), (180378, 'A beautiful face is temporary', 33184, 0), (180379, 'Pray for your needs, not your greed.', 5104, 0), (180380, 'Bitter love is better than sweet hate.', 5104, 0), (180381, 'Joy is God''s smile', 33185, 0), (180382, 'In shamanism it is not the jaguar or the crow that has meaning, it is what follows from whatever you view as an energetic transfer.', 20490, 0), (180383, 'Illusion (maya) cannot enter where there is ‘light’ (enlightenment, awareness). Once darkness falls, illusion will enter there. The Gnani Purush can arrange for your illusion to go away permanently.', 6286, 0), (180384, 'The greatest treasures are not found in museums, but in our hearts.', 24104, 0), (180385, 'Raise your love so high that anger cannot reach it.', 5104, 0), (180386, 'Suddenly (like walking into a light you know) you discover this: the certainty that nothing is certain, the deep relief of your own incredible smallness." (From "Even If You Could Explain It Completely")', 20497, 0), (180387, 'God is the world''s oldest poet', 33186, 0), (180388, 'If we had a penny for each time God smiled at us, we would all be billionaires.', 5104, 0), (180389, 'Each time a star twinkles, God is winking at the universe.', 24104, 0), (180390, 'The soul was the first temple', 33187, 0), (180391, 'God would not have brought you to this place to leave you here without the archangel''s help.', 4609, 0), (180392, 'All my relationships and all of my challenges are opportunities for my soul to evolve.', 4609, 0), (180393, 'Love is God''s shadow as He strolls through the universe.', 5104, 0), (180394, 'If God had a flower for each moment He thought of you, the whole universe would be a garden.', 5104, 0), (180395, 'If someone finds a flaw [shortcoming] in us, know that there is imperfection [defect] in us. However, it is a different matter if that person