d I get ''IT''? - By crying, begging, yelping! - Any of this helping?', 4618, 0), (180443, 'The soul’s steps are greater than the heart’s leaps.', 5104, 0), (180444, 'The heart smiles when the soul shines.', 5104, 0), (180445, 'Till the chit is in blissful state, the world does not come in one''s remembrance (one forgets the world till that time).', 6286, 0), (180446, 'Love is the brightest star in the soul''s sky.', 5104, 0), (180447, 'Self-acceptance is self-love in action.', 14390, 0), (180448, 'Letting go facilitates the evolution of the soul.', 14390, 0), (180449, 'To be sure, just because the darkness and the light are equally sacred does not mean we benefit by becoming complacent about the darkness we may meet in ourselves. Ultimately, if we are to cleanse the mirror of perception and purify ourselves, then we must bring light into the darkness. That’s always been the path of consciousness and the movement of illumination. This coexistence of darkness and light indeed creates a dance in which the clarity of light is invited to lead, but it does not create a hierarchy.', 12758, 0), (180450, 'Bricks on your back are easier to carry than pebbles on your soul.', 5104, 0);
INSERT INTO quotes (id, content, author_id, views) VALUES (180451, 'Spend every moment in "Hope" and "Love" for God for he has risen and brought us courage.', 5405, 0), (180452, 'It is warmer here. Can you see the light? Trust it. It is safe. It has lived a long time. It has seen much more than you. You fight a demon that you once knew but the demon is already slain. And from the corner of your eye you will see the scattered, sacred fire reform again. Settle, settle. Peace, peace', 4615, 0), (180453, 'Love in your heart is better than gold in your hands.', 5104, 0), (180454, 'The soul''s smile is better than the heart''s grin.', 5104, 0), (180455, 'Hope is the light that flickers and burns eternally, when you remain steadfast with faith.', 33193, 0), (180456, 'God has equipped me for battle, and is by my side leading me to victory.', 33193, 0), (180457, 'God has already been in your tomorrow, and is working on your today.', 33193, 0), (180458, 'A circumstance is not easy to come by and when it does, there are causes behind it. Therefore I do those things which bring an end to all the causes.', 6286, 0), (180459, 'Inner beauty magnifies outer beauty.', 5104, 0), (180460, 'A sweet soul will take you further than a sweet tongue.', 5104, 0), (180461, 'Love is the soul''s symphony.', 5104, 0), (180462, 'Calling upon the angels when we are in need, helps the angels fulfill their heavenly mission. We are truly co-creators with them.', 4609, 0), (180463, 'Make your mark in the world with divine ink: love.', 5104, 0), (180464, 'The greatest universe is the one within you.', 5104, 0), (180465, 'Love is the soul''s rainbow.', 5104, 0), (180466, 'Love poured out multiplies love poured in.', 5104, 0), (180467, 'God leaves footprints wherever He goes', 33194, 0), (180468, 'A heart''s wound heals quicker than a soul''s scratch.', 5104, 0), (180469, 'An ounce of love can overcome a mountain of fear.', 5104, 0), (180470, 'The greater your inner light the brighter your outer world.', 5104, 0), (180471, 'Love is who you are.', 19403, 0), (180472, 'Love is the highest prayer; as God is love, God cannot ignore Himself.', 5104, 0), (180473, 'Your inner light is your brightest light.', 5104, 0), (180474, 'Believe in yourself, because God''s angels sure do.', 4609, 0), (180475, 'To shine always love always.', 5104, 0), (180476, 'The most beautiful rainbow is the one inside your soul.', 5104, 0), (180477, 'The desire for connection with the Divine and our formless inner self is at the foundation of all desire for human connection.', 4615, 0), (180478, 'Angels don''t shout, they whisper.', 4609, 0), (180479, 'Your inner light lights up your outer world.', 5104, 0), (180480, 'Karma can be seen as a curse or a gift a curse because it keeps us attached to this world and a gift because it creates links with our loved ones it’s like a chain that binds us all together. Abdullah Fort', 33195, 0), (180481, 'The true instrument is that, with the help of which, the egoism and my-ness goes away.', 6286, 0), (180482, 'Your inner light is your inner power.', 5104, 0), (180483, 'The soul''s tears are worth more than the heart''s smiles.', 5104, 0), (180484, 'I just realized, there is too much of me in me.', 4571, 0), (180485, 'The golden door of harvest for the planet, it felt so ready to be opened ...', 33196, 0), (180486, 'Scriptures are as ‘helping problem’. Scriptures only give directions. Scriptures are like a thermometer. Can you grind a thermometer and give it as medicine?', 6286, 0), (180487, 'Whatever work you do in this world; the work itself has no value. If there is attachment-abhorrence behind that work, then only you are responsible for the next life. You are not responsible if attachment-abhorrence don’t occur.', 6286, 0), (180488, 'Ego will always conduct itself to make sure that it does not appear bad.', 6286, 0), (180489, 'God says only one thing if you want to have attachment towards worldly life; go ahead and get attached to it; or else, get attached to Me. If you get attached to Me, you will get permanent happiness and if you get attached to the worldly life, you will not find contentment!', 6286, 0), (180490, 'When attachment does not occur when someone gives flowers and no abhorrence occurs when someone throws stones', 33197, 0), (180491, 'If you want to go to moksha (attain ultimate liberation), you will have to become simple and straightforward. Being obstinate won’t work there. You will have to remove all the tubers; become totally free from intellect (abudh).', 6286, 0), (180492, 'If you deal obstinacy with obstinacy in this world', 33198, 0), (180493, 'One should not be obstinate even in worldly interaction. If you are obstinate with a ‘collector’, what will he do? He will throw you in jail. So then what will happen if you are obstinate with God? God won’t put you in jail, but his happiness upon you will break (will go away).', 6286, 0), (180494, 'What is it that doesn’t allow you to go to moksha? Obstinacy!', 6286, 0), (180495, 'Flowing egoism is not objectionable but if it is caught-up even a little-bit', 33199, 0), (180496, 'One is to cross this ocean in the form of obstinacy. We are standing on this side of obstinacy and we have to go to the other side. If someone becomes instrumental in removing your obstinacy; do not be disturbed about it, consider him to be extremely beneficial and undergo that experience with equanimity.', 6286, 0), (180497, 'Once the entrancement (Infatuation; Deluded state), in material objects, is gone; the loss in spirituality stops!', 6286, 0), (180498, 'If one has egoism without my-ness, he will go to moksha; all this entrapment is there because of egoism with my-ness!', 6286, 0), (180499, 'Gnani Purush’ (the enlightened one) is considered to be the owner of the whole universe. And yet, there is not the slightest egoism in Him. Where there is no authority, there is egoism and where there is authority, there is no egoism. This is the wonder of ‘Gnani Purush!’ ‘Gnani Purush’ is the manifest light.', 6286, 0), (180500, 'The worldly vision is filled with infinite infatuations and attachments and no one can escape from it', 33200, 0);
INSERT INTO quotes (id, content, author_id, views) VALUES (180501, 'Illusion (moha) is to take a beating and then forget, to take another beating and then forget again.', 6286, 0), (180502, 'When there is no attachment-abhorrence', 33201, 0), (180503, 'It is called equanimity when one has no attachment with the good (the auspicious) and no abhorrence for the bad (the inauspicious). The one without duality is in equanimity-state. In worldly interactions, people identify tolerance as equanimity!', 6286, 0), (180504, 'Equanimity means that one does not do abhorrence at the time of abhorrence (generating incidents) and one does not do attachment at the time of attachment (generating incidents).', 6286, 0), (180505, 'What does Jinmudra (Tirthankar God’s sitting posture) say? The lotus position of Vitrag Lords, one hand and foot placed over the other, preaches, “Oh, humans! Understand this if you have the wisdom. You have already brought with you the food, drink and all things you need; therefore, let go of the awareness that ‘I am the doer’ and make effort to attain Moksha (ultimate liberation)!', 6286, 0), (180506, 'The center of my sins stuck behind a blocked door, circled by hollow deeds spread on my lifetime’s floor', 2760, 0), (180507, 'Egoism devours all the energy, and in addition it makes one suffer.', 6286, 0), (180508, 'Where there is even the subtlest desire, the ‘Eternal Thing’ cannot be attained.', 6286, 0), (180509, 'Obstacles (antray) are indeed due to desires. As desires keep on decreasing, so do the obstructions (antray) keep on getting destroyed. Then, everything is acquired (at that stage).', 6286, 0), (180510, 'Why is it that ‘we’ (the Gnani Purush, the enlightened one) do not have any obstruction (antray)? It is because ‘we’ are in a desire-free state (Nirichchhak dasha).', 6286, 0), (180511, 'We’ (the Gnani Purush, the enlightened one) have only one desire, and that too is a discharging desire of doing ‘Jagat kalyan’ (world’s salvation).', 6286, 0), (180512, 'One who speaks ‘completely’ negative creates karmic obstructions (antray) and ‘positive’ does not create any obstruction (antray).', 6286, 0), (180513, 'Desires occur because pratyakhyan [resolutions to not repeat the mistake] were not done. It comes in the memory because pratikraman [repentances] were not done.', 6286, 0), (180514, 'Everything that is experienced through the five senses is all ‘discharge’. It is due to one’s merit karmas that everything works according to one’s wishes, but he claims, ‘I did it’ and when one faces losses, he will say, ‘God did it’ or ‘my horoscope is unfavorable’.', 6286, 0), (180515, 'Charge’ means coming together of all the circumstances and ‘discharge’ means the circumstances get over.', 6286, 0), (180516, 'It is called as ‘discharge’ (karma) when one has to do it compulsorily and against his wishes.', 6286, 0), (180517, 'As long as the awareness of ‘doer-ship’ is there, till then, one keeps on ‘charging’ (karma). In the Akram-path, ‘we’ (the Gnani Purush) destroy your doer-ship. The awareness that ‘I am the doer’ goes away and we give the understanding of ‘who the doer is’. Therefore, ‘charging’ (of karma) stops! What is left now? Only the ‘discharge’ is left.', 6286, 0), (180518, 'Where the ‘charging’ (of karma) stops, there lies the symptoms (signs) of attaining moksha.', 6286, 0), (180519, 'Importance is not in ‘discharge’ (of karmas) that occurs', 33202, 0), (180520, 'One’ is not a doer in this world. Where he believes that he is the doer, there is ‘charging’ (of karma). When one tastes egoistic pride of, “I did this samayik, I did these activities”, he will ‘charge’ (karma). The taste of egoistic pride is very sweet.', 6286, 0), (180521, 'Anger-pride-deceit-greed are in the form of ‘discharge’. But if one does not have ‘knowledge of True Self’ (realization of the self), then he ‘charges’ new karmas within.', 6286, 0), (180522, 'To run the worldly life, Egoism is not required. To bind [karma] for the next life, Egoism is required. If one doesn’t want the bondage for the next life, then also it is possible to conduct the worldly life without egoism. Entire worldly life is in the ‘discharge’ form. So it will continue to ‘discharge’ by itself.', 6286, 0), (180523, 'This is not suitable for me”- to say this is indeed madness, it is nothing but egoism. To say ‘will not suit’ is an offense.', 6286, 0), (180524, 'To say that, “I will not agree (will not accept)” is great egoism!', 6286, 0), (180525, 'To have a desire means to have dependency.', 6286, 0), (180526, 'Love transports mortal beings to the existential plane of spiritual eternity transcending the emotional, mental, and physical limitations of an inaccurately perceived finite existence.', 5043, 0), (180527, 'The Blessing #2:May love lead your eyes to look out for others,may love lead your ears to listen to others,may love lead your tongue to encourage others,may love lead your hands to help others,may love lead your mind to think of others,may love lead your heart to feel for others,and may love lead your soul to pray for others.', 5104, 0), (180528, 'The Blessing #1:May your eyes be profitable,may your ears be dutiful,may your tongue be insightful,may your hands be successful.May your mind be fruitful,may your heart be blissful,may your soul be joyful,may your life be peaceful.', 5104, 0), (180529, 'Gnan (knowledge of the Self) can never become agnan (knowledge other than the self, of relative world). It is called agnan only when the focused applied awareness of the Self changes.', 6286, 0), (180530, 'The person who wants to progress on the path of Vitrag (the enlightened ones), should keep the focus of the awareness to progress from the non-auspicious (bad) to the auspicious (good). And if one wants to go to final Liberation [moksha], he should keep ‘pure focus as the Self (Soul)’ (shuddha upayog). The person, who wants to go to Moksha, should not concern himself with the auspicious (good) or the inauspicious (bad). He should keep them both as the things to be cleared out.', 6286, 0), (180531, 'Who is considered as not living in the worldly life? The person who doesn’t have focus on the non-Self. ‘I’ (the Gnani Purush) do not live in the worldly life even for one moment. Liberation (Moksha) is to be found through the one who does not live in the worldly life. What can you not attain through the grace of such a person?', 6286, 0), (180532, 'Shukladhyan (pure contemplation of the Self, the Soul) is the direct cause for moksha (liberation). Dharmadhyan (auspicious contemplation; to hurt no one, give happiness to others) is the indirect cause for moksh (liberation). Artadhyan (inner mournful contemplation that hurts the self) is a cause for a birth in animal life form (non-human). Raudradhyan (wrathful contemplation that hurts the self and others) is a cause for a life in hell.', 6286, 0), (180533, 'Don''t seek, let go & what you are searching for will find you.', 21613, 0), (180534, 'I don''t have a problem with a world full of vampires and zombies but with one where the law forbids me from shooting them.', 18272, 0), (180535, 'We’ win over ‘negative’ with ‘positive’.', 6286, 0), (180536, 'Illusion means to weigh right and wrong with the same scale.', 6286, 0), (180537, 'If worries begin, then realize that the task at hand is going to be disturbed and if worries do not occur, then know that the task will not be disturbed. Worries are obstacles to the work.', 6286, 0), (180538, 'When it becomes above normal, material happiness will feel like misery.', 6286, 0), (180539, 'Fewer the necessities, better your life will be.', 6286, 0), (180540, 'Whole world is not looking for religion, it is looking for its own safe side.', 6286, 0), (180541, 'That what keeps us supported is dharma (religion).', 6286, 0), (180542, 'When does complete awareness occur? When the ego departs.', 6286, 0), (180543, 'Worrying is the greatest egoism!', 6286, 0), (180544, 'Where there is religion (religious following), there are no worries and where there are worries, there is no religion there.', 6286, 0), (180545, 'Actions do not need to be changed', 33203, 0), (180546, 'Spontaneous and natural (sahajik) speech means there is not an iota of ego in it.', 6286, 0), (180547, 'As one becomes increasingly unsteady (restless), one increases entanglements.', 6286, 0), (180548, 'Maintaining equanimity in misery is called penance (tapa).', 6286, 0), (180549, 'Self Effort (Purushartha) is that which will bear fruits, without fail.', 6286, 0), (180550, 'Moksha (ultimate liberation) means that you just have to change your vision.', 6286, 0);
INSERT INTO quotes (id, content, author_id, views) VALUES (180551, 'Worry is the greatest seed [cause] for the worldly life because worrying is the greatest egoism. If the egoism leaves, then worries will go away.', 6286, 0), (180552, 'Absence of conflict creating intents is itself Moksh (Ultimate Liberation).', 6286, 0), (180553, 'Difference of opinion is a clash, and to clash is a ‘weakness’.', 6286, 0), (180554, 'Gnani (The Enlightened one) means without Ego.', 6286, 0), (180555, 'While following religion, where ‘any thing’ is required, they are all called ‘relative’ paths.', 6286, 0), (180556, 'Where slightest of conflict exists, there is neither God nor Religion.', 6286, 0), (180557, 'Gnani Purush’ (The Enlightened one) is pure, so one becomes pure by just seeing him.', 6286, 0), (180558, 'As much longing for worldly happiness (of 5 senses) there is, that much less is the spiritual development.', 6286, 0), (180559, 'Religion has to be protected', 33204, 0), (180560, 'Unless therefore I am convinced by the testimony of Scripture or by the clearest reasoning, unless I am persuaded by means of the passages I have quoted, and unless they thus render my conscience bound by the word of God, I cannot and I will not retract, for it is unsafe for a Christian to speak against his conscience. Here I stand, I can do no other; may God help me. Amen."-Martin Luther', 4150, 0), (180561, 'Love in your mind gives you strength.Love in your heart gives you fortitude.Love in your soul gives you influence.Love in your life gives you power.', 5104, 0), (180562, 'When you walk around with a long face in the house, that is called conflict.', 6286, 0), (180563, 'If we clash with anyone, then it is our own weakness only.', 6286, 0), (180564, 'One is not to win the world, he has to win the home (family).', 6286, 0), (180565, 'Absence of worldly misery - that is called eternal bliss.', 6286, 0), (180566, '. . . the sole aim of Okinawa Karate is to teach A person to handle violence and violent individuals; whether it is tactile, mental or spiritual', 11124, 0), (180567, '. . . most martial artists want to know how A technique is done, A seasoned Sensei will demonstrate why', 11124, 0), (180568, 'An amber sunset, a flowing river, a snow capped mountain, a beautiful heart, a calm mind, deep eyes, the moon, the earth and the sky - they are all silent. It''s the words that give them meaning, decipher their essence and share their message.', 21795, 0), (180569, 'Good can exist without evil,but evil cannot exist without good.The former is eternal,the latter is temporal.', 5104, 0), (180570, 'The angels will help get you where you need to go.', 4609, 0), (180571, 'Personal integrity is about honoring yourself. Shifting from people pleasing and honoring your time, keeping your word to yourself, taking care of your needs, honoring personal and professional boundaries, honoring your goals and commitments that you made to yourself. Staying true to who you really are. Doing the right thing. Being kind and compassionate to others, being kind to you.', 4609, 0), (180572, 'If you ask God for love,He may give you someone to forgive.If you ask God for patience,He may give you someone to bear.', 5104, 0), (180573, 'We all have a mission. And that mission is to love ourselves, love each other, help one another and leave this world in a better place because we lived on it.', 4609, 0), (180574, 'Prayer creates a bridge from your heart to God.', 4609, 0), (180575, 'Laughter is a gift from God that opens the heart.', 4609, 0), (180576, 'Your heart has a deeper intelligence than your mind ever will.', 4609, 0), (180577, 'Some things must remain the same in order for the universe to flow properly. One pebble dashed out across the ocean leaves a lifetime of ripples. They call it the butterfly effect.', 33205, 0), (180578, 'Fools do not acknowledge God,the proud reject Him,the wise embrace Him,and the righteous worship Him.', 5104, 0), (180579, 'Spiritual battles have greater consequences than earthly wars.', 5104, 0), (180580, 'Welcome the righteous,avoid the wicked,and yet open both arms to the repentant.Whoever receives them receives God.', 5104, 0), (180581, 'Righteousness is light', 33206, 0), (180582, 'The slightest act of love holds greater spiritual power than a thousand rituals.', 5104, 0), (180583, 'One gains more from a fast than a feast.', 5104, 0), (180584, 'Your soul is like a flower and your spirit is the seed.As your spirit grows, the soul blossoms.', 19446, 0), (180585, 'Pray greatly.Pray gladly.Pray graciously.Pray gallantly.', 5104, 0), (180586, 'Pray patiently.Pray purposefully.Pray painstakingly.Pray perfectly.', 5104, 0), (180587, 'Pray daily.Pray daringly.Pray desperately.Pray determinedly.', 5104, 0), (180588, 'Pray sensibly.Pray scrupulously.Pray selflessly.Pray seriously.', 5104, 0), (180589, 'Love is RealWhat would we have for the world? Would we have it lost in darkness and hate or would we have it in the light of love? What we extend is what we see, extend love and it will grow to encompass all things. Love is real, hate, fear is not…repeat that over and over again...Love is real, I choose to see a world forgiven, I choose to see my brother as I see myself, loved beyond measure whole and holy, blessed…Look past the nightmare your brother believes real and see them for who they are, Holy Children of God pretending to be that which they are not.Love and Light', 33207, 0), (180590, 'Remember to take in and harvest light yet also allow yourself to cast shadows where needed, like a tree. Then, in return, your shadow will support your light.', 5745, 0), (180591, 'In strength the body only knows itself, is full of itself, its movements, its words, but in weakness is the invisible and the whisperings.', 8757, 0), (180592, 'Believe in the sacred word of God, the Holy Bible, with its treasury of inspiration and sacred truth; in the Book of Mormon as a testimony of the living Christ. Believe in the Church as the organization which the God of Heaven established for the blessing of His sons and daughters of all generations of time.', 197, 0), (180593, 'Our feelings are the wings of our intuition.', 14390, 0), (180594, 'Love and intuition are born of the same source. Of all the gifts you will receive in this life, love is the only one with everlasting power. Love is your companion in this world and into the next.', 14390, 0), (180595, 'On deathbed every single good, bad, ugly moment becomes special.', 26761, 0), (180596, 'The ''Mind'' in it''s nature is conditioned to ''label''. From people, to situations, and circumstances to everything in between. When we allow the mind to shut down we let things be as they are.', 11129, 0), (180597, 'Luck is the way the dust settles when God passes by.', 33208, 0), (180598, 'Take care to keep open house : Because in this way some have had angels as their guests, without being conscious of it ". Hebrews 13:2.', 33209, 0), (180599, 'No matter the circumstances, I encourage you to go forward with faith and prayer, calling on the Lord. You may not receive any direct revelation. But you will discover, as the years pass, that there has been a subtle guiding of your footsteps in paths of progress and great purpose.', 197, 0), (180600, 'The one who has found inner silence, stops pondering over the meaning of life and starts living it. That''s the journey from "going with the flow" to "being the flow.', 21795, 0);
INSERT INTO quotes (id, content, author_id, views) VALUES (180601, 'If somebody is terribly damaged, and has experienced great trauma as a child, so much so that a part of this child breaks off, so to speak, and never develops further than the incident and the only survival and coping skills available to that child at that time. Where does the responsibility lie? This man/child, woman/child is a sum of his/her experiences. Has the trauma stopped him/her from learning better ways or from wanting to learn better ways? Where does the conscience kick in? Where does the souls learning journey kick in? Are the fiend makers fiends of greater capacity than he, or is he less than their “monster made”? This is really serious stuff. What compulses and impulses this man/woman in this behaviour? Passed on behaviour patterns tend to worsen through the generations, unless a soul is born to them that has the capability to see beyond their levels of darkness, willing to forge a path into the light, using the experiences of suffering to enlighten and purify the way rather than the opposite.', 33210, 0), (180602, 'I acknowledge the challenge of believing in a supernatural divinity. After all, in the natural a rock is a rock; a desk is a desk; my skin is my skin. Or are they? That rock you pick up and feel on your skin and place on the desk is 99.9% empty space—between atoms; as is your skin and the desk. So, perhaps it is our perception of the natural or “real” world that needs tweaking, not the supernatural.', 5190, 0), (180603, 'Proving one’s innocence is as improbable as going to Pluto fora honeymoon. It could take away everything you had in life, dearones, dreams, hopes and, most importantly, the right to have yourfreedom.', 26761, 0), (180604, 'We are the authors of the stories our soul unfolds.', 14390, 0), (180605, 'A physical wound may heal, but a spiritual one may last for ever', 3682, 0), (180606, 'Being Mindful of our Feelings we will get Delighted. The Quality of Life is in proportion of our Capacity to Get Delighted and this is within our Capacity to Pay Attention. Be Aware of Synchronicity among All and Alert to the presence of Divine in All.', 5320, 0), (180607, 'Spirituality is not a religion or a trend—it is a lifestyle. It is a lifestyle of awareness that combines the understanding of faith, body, mind, and soul, allowing us to live modern-day enlightened lives in small and big ways.', 19423, 0), (180608, 'It''s life, it''s happening to you right now, what are going to do with your time here? Are you going to help people? are you going to chase your career, start a family or buy many properties; independently? Whatever it is, make a choice and do something with it - one thing is certain, most people die living their life, never a day before or after, only when their truly experiencing. That could be tomorrow, would you be proud of everything you became and achieved? If not, now is your second chance.', 3305, 0), (180609, 'Keep the dream alive and the heart open', 30731, 0), (180610, 'Lean on God, and he leans on you fulfilling his love on Earth.', 27288, 0), (180611, 'If we throw judgments out, that is exactly what will return to us. What we give is exactly what we will receive. It doesn’t matter if we throw out good or bad. It all comes back. It is a spiritual law.', 26505, 0), (180612, 'Do you actually think that you are in control of this world, think again for G-d has control what he allows is for a reason.', 33211, 0), (180613, 'Be careful that you do not forget your G-d.', 33211, 0), (180614, 'One would say You had not left me for a single instant. "Did you doubt it?', 33212, 0), (180615, 'Loss of worldly riches is better than loss of heavenly treasures.', 5104, 0), (180616, 'The wisest of the wicked schemes are actually foolish.', 19288, 0), (180617, 'The Present will remind you of a forgotten Truth. You are not the body or mind, but the loving, radiant, divine energy that is God. In the Present, you fulfill your destiny as a spiritual being.', 33213, 0), (180618, 'Travelling in other’s shoes is a complex process. Everyone carries loads of inherited virtues and then, heaps of experience acquired while travelling their own exclusive path of life. One’s personality, particularly the way one thinks, beholds both inborn traits and learned knowledge. Unless one is born to the same parents as the other, exactly at same time, beholding same blend of inherent traits and travelled the same path the other has travelled so far—a biological and pragmatic impossibility—it is imprudent to claim having knowledge of other’s thought process. One’s uniqueness is not constrained to the physical form, but is pertinent, too, to intellectual, emotional and spiritual forms.', 22224, 0), (180619, 'Love is the intoxication of God.', 27288, 0), (180620, 'Good luck is the expression of your divinity within.', 27288, 0), (180621, 'Within the moment of now, there is presence of ever there, As It is;, Invisible; Nothingness; of Still and silent awareness; in substratum; witnessing itself which U in real R...It has nothing to do with Your mind, Your body appearance and Your world...Wisdom is to let it recognize and and realize itself...Often in Ignorance of IT, ignorant start believing "In the Moment", "As It Is" words, which point towards IT (awareness), ignorantly for the appearing body, appearing mind and appearing creation...Be Happy and Keep Smiling...', 24966, 0), (180622, 'Your intuition won''t fail you, the quest dear; is to silence your mind so you can feel your way home.', 3305, 0), (180623, 'Your gift to the world is your purpose, you must find it, not for them, but for you. They will live on regardless of who you are, but you will remember who you felt short of, trying to please them. The only gift that the world needs is more, awakened beings, ready to be themselves, to unite a community to do the same; everywhere & that is the gift, to rise to your greatness & help others do the same.', 3305, 0), (